{"tid":807600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解無咩人覺得單數/雙數嚟啲設計好弱智","createTime":"2018-09-05T15:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T16:24:55.000Z","uid":200739,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0e114750b78caa8e3d8981fa0e277ecf3bfbb202","tid":807600,"uid":200739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T15:35:07.000Z","msg":"嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以我由細到大對嘅認知，就係將人由一個地方帶到另一個地方嘅方便工具，但我就點諗到諗唔明點解要發明單數同雙數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地嘅設計係令到你由一個地方只可以去到佢指定嘅層數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n見過有啲樓就有3部 , 其中一部就單數，另一部就雙數，最後一部就全部都去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你3部唔起都起左，横掂都係打通晒全座樓，點解就要分一單一雙咁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你3部都全部去到晒所有樓層唔得？<br />\n<br />\n睇到嚟到就實有人講啲咩容易啲分散人流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明就快分散人流嘅方法就係全部所有樓層都去，假設用返啱啱嗰3部做例子，例如突然有一大班人要上某單數樓層，而只係單數同去全層部係入唔晒，其他人就要等嚟2部上完再落返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等部雙數就全程on99咁無郁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明顯如果3部都去全層先係最快最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n更加唔洗講有啲樓要用完一部上再轉另一部再上嚟啲設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到底係邊個發明嚟啲設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eaa05793f59a145c8a4daea485c0eceadda4136","tid":807600,"uid":65774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T15:36:48.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪未番過工或者未番過學？"},{"pid":"2c84c6549adf5cb7276f7d38a5a95f2fbbbb32f3","tid":807600,"uid":200739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7eaa05793f59a145c8a4daea485c0eceadda4136","tid":807600,"uid":65774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T15:36:48.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪未番過工或者未番過學？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime"